                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-1021" type="given" value="JESSE"></interp>JESSE M'PHERSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my father, in White Horse-street, Step<lb></lb>ney. I keep a fruit-stall at the comer of Exmouth-street—on the 21st of October I was sitting at my stall opposite, and saw a man take a coat from a chair outside the prosecutor's shop—when I sailed to him he threw it down on the curb—I called, "Stop thief I"—I after that told Mr. Corner where it was, and he got it.</p>
